{"type":"message","id":"53075394","parentId":"0d3acf63","timestamp":"2026-03-25T04:41:38.530Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Both grep commands returned no matches (exit code 1). Let me try a simpler approach - just show what files are NOT session garbage or sensitive, so I can determine what's safe to commit.\n\nActually, the issue is that almost ALL the modified files are either session files, cron runs, or sensitive. Let me just show the user the clean picture of what's happening and suggest a resolution.\n\nThe key problem is:\n1. There are ~53 tracked modified/deleted files - mostly session artifacts and sensitive files\n2. There are ~920 untracked files - mostly session garbage\n3. Only a few files are genuinely safe to commit: models.json, jobs.json, sessions.json, openclaw.json, bridge_state.json, coding-agent.sqlite, mirror_state.json, weibo scripts, subagents/runs.json, workspace\n\n\n4. For untracked files, it's even messier - those deleted session files aren't taking up space, but there are still hundreds of active session JSONLs cluttering the repository\n\nThis really needs a proper cleanup with .gitignore updates rather than just selective commits, but given the time constraints and that the backup is already blocked for safety reasons, I'll present the situation clearly to the user and recommend a practical path forward.","thinkingSignature":"5d7b00fae5e75734e3fb879d0a323405ec2caa6b722e429062908462bd76fd05"},{"type":"text","text":"今天的定期巡检整体结论：**量化主链无异常，09:15 已全部 PASS**。但有一件需要处理的事：\n\n**Workspace backup 仍处于 BLOCKED 状态**\n\n原因很清楚：\n- 53个已跟踪修改/删除的文件里，大部分是**会话垃圾**（已删除的session日志、重置记录）\n- 920个未跟踪文件里，**大量是运行时产物**（session JSONL、cron run 日志）\n- 还有 `auth-profiles.json` 和 `device-auth.json` 两个敏感文件，直接 `git add -A` 风险太高\n\n建议下一步（需要你授权）：我可以帮你做一个**安全的定向清理+分批提交**，大致思路：\n1. 更新 `.gitignore`，把 `sessions/`, `cron/runs/`, `*.deleted.*`, `*.reset.*` 等会话产物正式排除\n2. 敏感文件单独处理（不进 git）\n3. 确认安全后，按类型分批 commit：\n   - 配置文件（`models.json`、`openclaw.json`、`jobs.json`）\n   - Workspace 内容\n   - 脚本与技能\n\n这样既能保护敏感信息，又能保持 config 变更可追溯。\n\n是否授权我执行这个清理方案？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":9784,"output":505,"cacheRead":38441,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48730,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774413685616}}
